file.content:
export XDG_CONFIG_HOME=$HOME/.config
export PATH="$HOME/.local/bin:$HOME/go/bin:$PATH"
PATH="/Users/dhamidi/Applications/Visual Studio Code.app/Contents/Resources/app/bin/:$PATH"
PATH="/opt/homebrew/Cellar/tcl-tk/9.0.2/bin:$PATH"
export EDITOR=nvim
eval "$(/opt/homebrew/bin/brew shellenv bash)"
for f in /opt/homebrew/etc/profile.d/*; do
  source "$f"
done
# bun
export BUN_INSTALL="$HOME/.bun"
export PATH="$BUN_INSTALL/bin:$PATH"
if ! [[ -w "$HOME/.ssh/agent.sock" ]]; then
  eval "$(ssh-agent -a $HOME/.ssh/agent.sock -s)"
fi
eval "$(starship init bash)"
source /opt/homebrew/etc/bash_completion
export AMP_API_KEY=$(key get amp.ampcode)
#export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=$(key get claude)
export MANPAGER='nvim +Man!'
export MANPATH="/opt/homebrew/share/man/:$MANPATH"
eval "$(fzf --bash)"

# history
export LESSOPEN="|lessopen %s"
export HISTSIZE=100000
shopt -s lithist
PROMPT_COMMAND="$PROMPT_COMMAND;history -a"

# pnpm
export PNPM_HOME="/Users/dhamidi/Library/pnpm"
case ":$PATH:" in
*":$PNPM_HOME:"*) ;;
*) export PATH="$PNPM_HOME:$PATH" ;;
esac
# pnpm end

# The next line updates PATH for the Google Cloud SDK.
if [ -f '/Users/dhamidi/google-cloud-sdk/path.bash.inc' ]; then . '/Users/dhamidi/google-cloud-sdk/path.bash.inc'; fi

# The next line enables shell command completion for gcloud.
if [ -f '/Users/dhamidi/google-cloud-sdk/completion.bash.inc' ]; then . '/Users/dhamidi/google-cloud-sdk/completion.bash.inc'; fi

eval "$(mise activate bash)"
eval "$(agg completion bash)"
# less
export LESS=-R
export LESSOPEN="|lessopen %s"
export VSCODE_USER_SETTINGS="$HOME/Library/Application Support/Code/User/settings.json"
export SRC_ENDPOINT=https://sourcegraph.com
export SRC_ACCESS_TOKEN=sgp_e3cb05880bc40429_48a83fa49226ef3dc659da38c3d307e4be51fb65
export AMP_CONNECT=1

export PATH=/Users/dhamidi/.sg:$PATH
